<scopecontent>
<p>This volume documents the monies paid to the delegates. It lists funds for traveling, orders, wages, as well as supplies purchased for the Contintental Army. Of note are the different currencies listed such as Virginia or Pennsylvania currency, as well as the accounts of notable delegates such as Thomas Jefferson, Richard Henry and Francis Lightfoot Lee.
</p>
</scopecontent>
